org.openadaptor.auxil.processor.xml
Class XsltProcessor

java.lang.Object
  org.openadaptor.core.Component
      org.openadaptor.auxil.processor.xml.XsltProcessor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Administrable, IComponent, IDataProcessor
public class XsltProcessor
extends Component
implements IDataProcessor

Applies the XSLT defined in the properties to the record and returns the result as an String.

Can support transforms on either XML String or dom4j document records.

Uses the dom4j library to apply the transform

Author:
Russ Fennell
